text: Courage of Lassie is a 1946 American drama movie directed by Fred M. Wilcox and is the third movie in the Lassie series. It stars Elizabeth Taylor, Frank Morgan, Selena Royle, Catherine McLeod, Frank Morgan, Tom Drake, Garry Owen, Harry Davenport and was distributed by Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1946 drama movies Category:1946 war movies Category:American war movies Category:1940s American drama movies Category:MGM movies
title: Courage of Lassie
